rt. Beautifully illustrated with more than 140 paintings and drawings, this book serves as an essential reference on Seurat.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Apr 2020) 0aNeo-impressionism (Art) 0aNeo-impressionism (Art). 0aVisual perception in art. 7aART / Individual Artists / Monographs.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300212822423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300212822.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO